room_title: Escape room "Spy Chambers" by The Clue Room in Denver
room_description:
A spy ring has been operating in Denver and is responsible for the disappearance of 12 agents. Your team of highly trained intelligence officers has been called in to help break up this spy organization. To do that, you will need to match wits with the spy organization to break numerous codes, riddles and puzzles so that they may be captured!
For groups between 10-12 players, two separate Spy Chamber game rooms are available where players will compete head-to-head.
